siteMetadata.subtitle: A blog about stuff that I like

markdownRemark.html:
I’m Logan, a recent graduate from the University of Pennsylvania where I studied cognitive science and computer science in the College of Arts & Sciences. I will begin work as a software engineer for Lutron Electronics in January 2020. I enjoy reading, traveling, music, television, and many other things.

Find me on Wastebook, follow me on Twitter, and connect with me on LinkedIn.
